<plot>Perky Idea's innovative educational feature documentary reveals a creative montage of interviews from noted professional artist in the African-American Community. This fresh yet poignant tale reaches into the past to carve an exciting future, Thea-Marie Perkins' 70-minute feature documentary exposes where theater is today, shares it's past, and offers a serious look at crafting the future for a younger generation.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?073632</url></doc>
